author: Home Repair Tutor
description: ZipWall reusable dust barrier tips…I’m remodeling this bathroom and want to seal off the work site. The ZipWll ZipSheet is a great option because it’s big, reusable, and has a built-in zipper door. When combined with a few poles this sets up fast and keeps dust out of the rest of the home.
